  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Authorizes the town of Johnston, if an aggregate of two hundred fifty (250) or more units should be proposed in comprehensive permit project(s), to enact an emergency moratorium until the permit requirement of \u00a7 45-53-4 are amended."
